    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayed-ali-raza"
    ],
    "verses": [
      {
        "index": 2231,
        "local_index": 1,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:458:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/414/515",
        "text": [
          "٤١٤. وَفِي خَبَرٍ آخَرَ أَنَّهُ (عليه السلام) قَالَ لِلْأَشْعَثِ بْنِ قَيْسٍ مُعَزِّياً (عَنِ ابْنٍ لَهُ)"
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "414. In another tradition it is related that Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said to al-Ash‘ath ibn Qays by way of condolence on the death of his son:"
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 2232,
        "local_index": 2,
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:458:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/414/516",
        "text": [
          "إِنْ صَبَرْتَ صَبْرَ الْأَكَارِمِ، وَإِلَّا سَلَوْتَ سُلُوَّ الْبَهَائِمِ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "Either endure like great people or else you will forget like animals."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
